asset.hookText:
Everything you need to know about the latest epilator from Braun, the Silk Epil 7 SkinSpa Epilation & Exfoliation System (7931).  This unique epilating system comes with an exfoliating brush attachment to prepare the skin for epilation, for smoother, visibly refined skin.  This video includes all the caps and attachments that are included in the package, how to use them, how to charge the device and tips for exfoliation and epilation.  Thanks for watching!

Full blog post here
